longBusinessSummary: Optec International, Inc. engages in selling and marketing optimized fuel maximizer units in North America and internationally. It markets optimized fuel maximizer for passenger vehicles, intermediate/medium duty trucks, off-road equipment, generator systems, heavy duty diesel on-road vehicles, and transportation refrigeration units. The company was formerly known as Green Meadow Products, Inc. and changed its name to Optec International, Inc. in August 2017. Optec International, Inc. was founded in 2012 and is based in Carlsbad, California.
